      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A creature that hits the pudding with a melee attack roll takes 4 (1d8) dano de ácido. Nonmagical ammunition is destroyed immediately after hitting the pudding and dealing any de dano. Any nonmagical weapon takes a cumulative -1 penalty to attack rolls immediately after dealing de dano to the pudding and coming into contact with it. The weapon is destroyed if the penalty reaches -5. The penalty can be removed by casting the Mending spell on the weapon.\nIn 1 minute, the pudding can eat through 0,6 m of nonmagical wood or metal.</p>",
